data.title: Chief Bear Hart
data.meta_description: Chief Bear William Jackson Hart is my 9th great uncle and was 3/4 Cherokee. i am working on my genealogy and would like to find what my percentage is. his mother was Nancy Bauer. Chief Bear was born in Cherokee Alabama in 1660. he died in 1717 in Cherokee Alabama.
